<hr color="#660066" size="20"><a id="fus_63" name=""><br>
<div align="center">
<center>
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse" width="80%">
<tr>
<td width="100%">
<font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">Staff of Elemental Essence</font><font size="2"> - 09-22-2004 19:01</font><br><br></td>
