<tr>
<td width="100%"><font size="2">Congratulations to Celecar on the Mithaniel Marr server for being the first magician to wield the Magician 1.5 Epic, the Staff of Elemental Essence&#33;<br><br><P><img src=/library/epic2/images/mage_epic_15.jpg></font><br><br></td>
